To build the app, follow these steps:

1. Clone the repo
2. Cd into the repo directory
3. Create a virtual environment (`python -m venv venv`)
4. Install the dependencies (`pip install -r requirements.txt`)
todo: fix pyinstaller build not properly including the asset images
5. Build the app (`pyinstaller --noconfirm --onedir --windowed --add-data "venv/Lib/site-packages/customtkinter;customtkinter/" --add-data "assets;assets/"  main.py`)
